nodes.text: During the Clone Wars, the Trade Federation Home Defense Legions of the Separatist Alliance's navy maintained an enormous fleet of Lucrehulk-class Battleships in the Quellor sector. The fleet fought against the Galactic Republic's 2nd Fleet during the Republic's blockade of the sector.
The Quellor sector fleet was mentioned in Rise of the Separatists, a roleplaying supplementary sourcebook for the Star Wars Roleplaying series that was published by Fantasy Flight Games in 2019.
